<item>
            <title>[LU-14984] ASSERTION( atomic_read(&amp;conn-&gt;c_refcount) &gt; 1 )</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14984</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A system a client has two interfaces, one on o2ib1 and another on o2ib. Attempt to create two mount points on each of the networks. Mounting on o2ib succeeds. Mounting on o2ib1 results in the assert&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
 Message from syslogd@gb005 at Sep 1 21:52:38 ...
 kernel:LustreError: 1988:0:(connection.c:96:ptlrpc_connection_put()) ASSERTION( atomic_read(&amp;amp;conn-&amp;gt;c_refcount) &amp;gt; 1 ) failed:Message from syslogd@gb005 at Sep 1 21:52:38 ...
 kernel:LustreError: 1988:0:(connection.c:96:ptlrpc_connection_put()) LBUG&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A similar assert was reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6991&quot; title=&quot;LBUG in ptlrpc_connection_put(): ASSERTION( atomic_read(&amp;amp;conn-&amp;gt;c_refcount) &amp;gt; 1 )&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6991&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6991&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but was not reproducible. That ticket was closed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
